         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832"><!-- p3l1-r5 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De meditatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
      ¶ De meditatione. Rubrica i.<!-- dbcheck; this seems like 5 -->
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>SAlomon in eccl. c. 12. et
      <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>sin. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e127">Frequens
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>Bmeditatio carnis est afflictio.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e137">¶ Aristoteles de memoria et remis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>Meditationes memoriam saluant in remini
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>scendo: hoc autem nil est alterum quam speculari.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>multotiens sicut imaginem: et non sicut per se </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e152">¶ Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 30. Ante tem
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>pus senectam adducit cogitatus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e162">¶ Mattheus in euangel. c. 6. Ubi est thesau
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>rus tuus: ibi et cor tuum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e172">¶ Seneca de ira li. 2. Nihil est difficile et ar
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>duum quod non humana mens vincat: et in sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>miliaritatem perducat assidua cogitatio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e184">¶ Uegecius de re militari lib. i. ti. 19. Nihil
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>est quod non assidua medicatio facillimum red
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>dat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e192"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e194"> Libro. 2 ti. 23. et pe. Antiqua est pru
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>densque sententia omnea artes in meditatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>ne consistere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46832-Qd1e206">¶ Prouerb. vulg. Chi a porcel perdu: spesse
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>fiae ge rore al cul. </quote>
            </p>
    
         </div>
